oker)|3R]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[1995 Grand Prix (snooker)|3R]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[1996 Grand Prix (snooker)|1R]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[1997 Grand Prix (snooker)|1R]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#ffebcd;\"|[[1998 Grand Prix (snooker)|QF]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[1999 Grand Prix (snooker)|1R]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2000 Grand Prix (snooker)|3R]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:thistle;\"|[[2001 LG Cup (snooker)|F]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2002 LG Cup (snooker)|2R]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2003 LG Cup (snooker)|2R]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2004 Grand Prix (snooker)|3R]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2005 Grand Prix (snooker)|2R]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2006 Grand Prix (snooker)|RR]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#ffebcd;\"|[[2007 Grand Prix (snooker)|QF]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2008 Grand Prix (snooker)|2R]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#ffebcd;\"|[[2009 Grand Prix (snooker)|QF]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:yellow;\" |[[2010 World Open (snooker)|SF]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"| LQ\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2013 World Open (snooker)|1R]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"|LQ\n|  colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"| Not Held\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2016 World Open (snooker)|1R]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2017 World Open (snooker)|3R]] \n| style=\"text-align:center; background:#afeeee;\"|[[2018 World Open (snooker)|1R]]\n| style=\"text-align:center; color:#ccc;\"| WD\n|-\n|style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\"| [[Northern Ireland Open (snooker)|Northern Ireland O