ober 30, 2010}}</ref> and ran until November 21, 2010.<ref name=\"Means\">{{Cite news |last=Means |first=Sean P. |title=Spend Halloween with the \"Sister Wives\" |work=[[The Salt Lake Tribune]] |date=October 22, 2010 |url=http://www.sltrib.com/sltrib/blogs/vulture/50525311-56/halloween-oct-season-sister.html.csp |accessdate=October 30, 2010}}</ref><ref name=\"France112asss  meri is cute 0\" /> The series has been renewed for a second season, which began March 2011.<ref>{{cite news |last=Pierce |first=Scott D. |title=TLC renews 'Sister Wives' |work=[[The Salt Lake Tribune]] |date=October 29, 2010 |url=http://www.sltrib.com/sltrib/news/50568032-78/wives-tlc-kody-sister.html.csp |accessdate=October 30, 2010}}</ref> The second season continued on September 25, 2011.<ref>{{cite web|title=TLC's 'Sister Wives' Returns With A Special Delivery|url=http://press.discovery.com/us/tlc/press-releases/2011/tlcs-sister-wives-returns-special-delivery-15-1509/|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111003035549/http://press.discovery.com/us/tlc/press-releases/2011/tlcs-sister-wives-returns-special-delivery-15-1509/|archivedate=October 3, 2011}}</ref> The third season debuted on May 13, 2012,<ref>{{cite press release|title=\"Sister Wives\" Season 3 Premieres Sunday, May 13th on TLC|url=http://thefutoncritic.com/news/2012/05/01/sister-wives-season-3-premieres-sunday-may-13th-on-tlc-28214/20120501tlc03/|work=The Futon Critic|date=May 1, 2012}}</ref> with the fourth-season premiere on July 21, 2013.<ref>{{cite web|last=Kondolojy|first=Amanda|title='Sister Wives' Returns for a Fourth Season on TLC|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2013/07/02/sister-wives-returns-for-a-fourth-season-on-tlc/190033/|work=TV by the Numbers|accessdate=July 29, 2013|date=July 2, 2013|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130706182306/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2013/07/02/sister-wives-returns-for-a-fourth-season-on-tlc/190033/|archivedate=July 6, 2013}}</ref>\n\n== S